        </item>
        <item>
            <title>FUJIFILM instax mini 41 即影即有相機，經典復古外形 + 升級近拍體驗</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/29/fujifilm-instax-mini-41/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fujifilm-instax-mini-41</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/29/fujifilm-instax-mini-41/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 29 Apr 2025 09:20:43 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[fujifilm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fujifilm Instax]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fujifilm instax mini 41]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Instax]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1304992</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>富士推出新一代入門即影即有相機 instax mini 41，作為人氣型號 mini 40 的後繼機種，延續經典復古設計之餘，亦針對用戶需求進行多項升級。全新型號保留黑色與深銀色的優雅外觀，更以橙色作細節點綴，呈現出時尚與懷舊兼備的美學風格。作為一部入門即影即有相機，instax mini 41 特別適合入門新手用家，不論是日常生活、旅行出遊、朋友聚會，皆可隨時記錄眼前場景，將回憶化為可觸可感的實體照片。無論是作為日常配搭的小巧相機，抑或作為饋贈親友的精緻禮品，mini 41 都展現出其兼具實用與美感的獨特魅力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305013" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00647-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00647-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00647.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>保留經典外形，橙色點綴更 Sharp 醒</h2><p>instax mini 41 延續 mini 40 一貫的復古造型設計，機身以黑色與深銀色作為主調，輔以細緻的橙色線條點綴，呈現出低調而不失個性的時尚風格。整體外觀揉合復古與現代感，無論是日常穿搭，還是出席特別場合時攜帶，都能輕鬆展現個人品味，成為造型焦點。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305006" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00640-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00640-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00640.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲延續 mini 40 復古造型設計</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305005" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00639-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00639-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00639.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00643-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00643-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00643.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲菲林計數器</p><p>相機下半部分採用細膩的紋理處理，不但增強握持手感，亦提高使用時的穩定性。無論是掛在胸前，還是單手操作拍攝，均具備良好的便攜性與實用性，方便用戶隨時隨地捕捉生活中的每一刻。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305004" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00638-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00638-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00638.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下半部分採用細膩的紋理處理</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305012" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00646-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00646-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00646.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲增強握持手感</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305008" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00642-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00642-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00642.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機背設有 thumb rest</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305010" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00644-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00644-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00644.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲惟一要彈是 mini 41 和上一代一樣不設腳架孔</p><h2>近拍模式 + 自拍鏡，影得埋自己都咁靚</h2><p class="" data-start="43" data-end="152">instax mini 41 特別新增了「近拍模式」，用戶只需旋轉鏡頭即可切換，無論拍攝特寫物件或進行自拍，操作均十分簡便。</p><p data-start="43" data-end="152"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305011" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00645-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00645-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00645.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="43" data-end="152"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305007" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00641-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00641-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00641.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-start="43" data-end="152">▲旋轉鏡頭環即可調校至近攝模式</p><p class="" data-start="43" data-end="152">鏡頭旁設有小巧的自拍鏡，方便用戶即時確認畫面構圖，避免拍攝時出現臉部偏移或畫面裁切不當的情況。</p><p data-start="43" data-end="152"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00636-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00636-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00636.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305023" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc006382-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc006382-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc006382.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲自拍鏡</p><p class="" data-start="154" data-end="252">此外近拍模式亦支援「視差修正功能」，當用戶透過取景框構圖時，畫面會自動對應實際成像範圍，大大減少構圖誤差。即使是第一次使用即影即有相機，也能輕鬆掌握畫面中心，拍出對位準確、效果理想的近距離照片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305024" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042574809-694x467.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="467" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042574809-694x467.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042574809.jpg 1203w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/29/fujifilm-instax-mini-41/dc/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
